**Don’t hide embroidery/screen print** — use it as *why you’re credible for gifts*.

| What buyers think | What you want them to think |
|-------------------|-----------------------------|
| “Another promo company with a catalog” | “They curate gifts and handle production in-house” |
| “Swag = cheap pens and koozies” | “Gifting = thoughtful packages for people who matter” |
