**Working positioning line (you can refine in chat):**

> **Corporate gifting programs, curated and produced in-house** — embroidery, screen print, and full-color decoration for companies who want gifts that feel intentional, not leftover swag.

**Rebrand path:** Keep **Logo Clothing Shop** live now; introduce **Stitch & Stone Co.** in footer/About (“A new name for the same craft”) so you’re not throwing away SEO or existing relationships. When you rebrand, 301 old URLs to new ones.

**Money on the table — you’re right:** Promo is price-competitive. **Gifting** is budgeted differently (HR, marketing, executive assistants, client retention). Buyers pay for **time saved, taste, and reliability** — your consulting angle is the product.

